1) Dependencies

You need to have installed the cppunit framework. Check wether the libcppunit is in
/usr/local/lib
If not change the path to libcppunit in the test_runner.pro

2) How to extend the Unit-Tests

A) Create a MyTests.h file for the tests. Use the existing tests as a template.

B) Implement the tests in MyTests.cpp file.
It is important to register the testsuite in the test registry with:
CPPUNIT_TEST_SUITE_REGISTRATION ( MyTests )

C) Add the MyTests.h and MyTests.cpp file to the test_runner.pro
Also add the source files which will be tested to the test_runner.pro in HEADERS and SOURCES!

D) qmake + make

E) run: test_runner

F) Check the problems found :-))

Heinz
